title: Grateful Dead Live at Hartford Civic Center on 1981-03-14
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Sugaree, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Peggy-O-> CC Rider, Althea, Passenger, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Alabama Getaway-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Ship of Fools, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> I Need A Miracle-> Bertha-> Good Lovin', E: One More Saturday Night

reviews.review_text: Excellent AUD NEARLY a 5-star, especially the 1st set.
God's Work (the Wizard Jim Wise) ...is done through mystery, unknown conclusions. However, the journey is always what gets us there. Lest we forget the blood that was spiLLed...
